CustomField.description: This field specifies in text the borrower’s or co-borrower’s Other Hispanic or Latino ethnicity(ies) if 14 (Other Hispanic or Latino) is entered. Otherwise, leave this data field blank.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If Other Hispanic or Latino is selected as an Ethnicity, this text field allows you to specify the Other Hispanic or Latino ethnicity(ies). You may enter up to 50 characters.
CustomField.label: Hispanic or Latino Ethnicity(ies) Desc
